# Cursor Rules for BizFin Pro Website

## Project Overview
This is a WordPress financial consulting website with advanced AI integration, specializing in bank guarantees, tenders, and business financial services.

## Key Technologies
- WordPress 6.8.3 with Astra theme
- 29 active plugins + 16 must-use plugins
- OpenAI GPT-4 integration via Dutch proxy
- Advanced SEO with Yoast Premium
- Elementor page builder
- AI content generation and image creation

## Project Structure
- `wordpress/` - WordPress core files
- `wordpress/wp-content/plugins/` - 29 active plugins
- `wordpress/wp-content/mu-plugins/` - 16 must-use plugins
- `wordpress/wp-content/themes/` - Astra theme + custom theme
- `documentation/` - Comprehensive project documentation
- `scripts/` - Deployment and maintenance scripts

